item.content:encoded:
LSM consulting

Learn More

Let us help you stay safe

We provide our expertise to companies that want to keep safe in the cyberspace. Cyberattacks are malicious activities that compromise computer systems. They include malware attacks, phishing, denial-of-service attacks, man-in-the-middle attacks, and SQL injection attacks. Protecting against cyberattacks requires regular updates, strong passwords, secure networks, employee training, and security tools. Staying informed about cyber threats is crucial for maintaining digital security.

Implementing robust cybersecurity measures is crucial in today's digital age. Updating software, using strong passwords, and employee training programs can help protect sensitive information and prevent unauthorized access. Prioritizing cybersecurity is essential to safeguard data and maintain its confidentiality, integrity, and availability. We can help you be safe in this everchanging enviroment.

Cyber security testing

IT asset management

Cyber Security training

Understanding of Cyberattacks

“It takes 20 years to build a reputation and few minutes of cyber-incident to ruin it.”

Stephane Nappo

“Technology trust is a good thing, but control is a better one.”

Stephane Nappo

Understanding DDoS Attacks

DDoS (Distributed Denial of Service) attacks are malicious cyber-attacks that aim to overwhelm a website or network by flooding it with traffic. Attackers use compromised computers to generate a massive volume of requests, making the target inaccessible to legitimate users. DDoS attacks have serious consequences, and organizations should take proactive measures to defend against them. Stay informed about cybersecurity trends and implement strong security measures to mitigate the risk.

Malware

short for malicious software, is designed to harm, exploit, or infiltrate computer systems without user consent. It includes viruses, worms, trojans, ransomware, and spyware. Protect against malware by using antivirus software, keeping software updated, and practicing safe online habits. Regular backups are also important. Stay vigilant to minimize the risk of malware attacks.

Ransomware

is malicious software that encrypts files and demands a ransom for their release. It spreads through phishing emails, downloads, or software vulnerabilities. Stay cautious, back up files, and keep your software up to date to minimize the risk of falling victim to ransomware attacks.

Social engineering

is a technique used by cyber attackers to manipulate individuals into revealing sensitive information or compromising their security. It involves exploiting human psychology, like trust or curiosity, to deceive victims. Beware of unsolicited requests and be vigilant against social engineering attacks.

With an evergrowing cyberspace the importance of safety for business is becoming imperative

Confidentiality

We do not disclouse client details and or other information as a priority for safety and privacy. We guarantee confidentiality to protect our clients via NDA or any other measure our clients find necessary

Learn More

Professionalism

Years of expertise in various IT fields gives us a unique ability to understand various Cyber enviroments and setups so we can ensure the optimal solution for your needs.

Learn More

Expertise

Our wide range of experience and deep knowledge allows us to understnasd each and every clients needs, and create tailormade solutions to best suite their needs.

item.title: Services
item.dc:creator: matejbonin
item.content:encoded:
"Risk management isn't rocket science - it's much more complicated"

John Adams

what we offer to our clients

Cyber security consulting

Cyber security consulting services help businesses strengthen their defenses against cyber threats. This is particularly important in small and medium companies sicne the resources that they can allocate to cyber security are limited. Consultants assess vulnerabilities, recommend solutions, and educate employees. By leveraging experts, organizations can protect assets, maintain trust, and minimize the impact of cyber attacks.

Asset management solutions

IT asset management solutions are essential for businesses to track, monitor, and maintain their IT assets. These solutions offer features like inventory management, asset tracking, software license management, and cost optimization. They help organizations streamline asset lifecycles, manage security risks, and gain valuable insights through reporting and analytics.

Penetration test

Penetration testing, or ethical hacking, is a cybersecurity practice that involves simulating real-world attacks to uncover vulnerabilities in computer systems, networks, or applications. It helps identify weaknesses, assess potential consequences, validate security controls, and improve overall security. Ethical hackers conduct thorough testing to strengthen defenses and protect sensitive data.

Cyber security training

Cybersecurity training is crucial for protecting against online threats. Key points include building awareness, best practices, recognizing phishing attacks, secure online behavior, and incident response. Ongoing training and vigilance are essential for maintaining a strong security posture. Stay safe online!

Case Studies

Case Study A

as a small company we struggle to secure our business. LSM helped us understand the basics and together we built an efficient setup baesd around our employes and partners. no need for big investment just a tailored approch to the issues at hand.

Case Study B

We built our security system years ago and we needed a fresh prospective on the possible threats. Finding vulnerabilities is key to ensuring a secure enviroment.

item.title: Our Mission and priciples
item.dc:creator: matejbonin
item.content:encoded:
Once the importance of providing a secure enviroment is acknwoledged by the company's management or owners, a lot of effort and resources have to be allocated to ensure cyber security. Financial, technical, and human resources that are hard to find and develope even for the biggest and most experienced companies. The challenges that big, medium and small compaines are facing regarding cyber securty are verey different. We made it our mission to help our clients secure their working enviroment regardless of their size and experience. We firmly believe that helping companies stay safe, will bring the neccesary stability to allow the growth and development needed for the to thrive in their markets and fields.

Confidetiality

We completely understand the significance of instilling trust in our clients when it comes to sharing their valuable information with us. As a dedicated and reliable partner, we recognize the importance of providing a safe and secure environment for our clients' data. Our top priority is to ensure that all the information entrusted to us is handled with the utmost care and safeguarded against any potential threats or breaches. With advanced security measures in place, robust encryption protocols, and stringent data protection policies, we strive to create a fortress-like system to guarantee the confidentiality, integrity, and availability of our clients' information. Rest assured, we are committed to maintaining the highest standards of security to give our clients peace of mind.

Professionalism

We distinguish ourselves in the IT industry through our unwavering commitment to professionalism. With a focus on technical excellence, ethical conduct, effective communication, problem-solving skills, continuous professional development, and a client-centric approach, we deliver exceptional results. Trust us to handle your IT needs with the utmost professionalism.

Expertise

Our extensive expertise in the IT industry sets us apart from the competition. With years of experience and a deep understanding of the latest technologies, we are able to provide innovative solutions tailored to meet the unique needs of our clients. Whether it's developing cutting-edge software, implementing robust cybersecurity measures, or providing comprehensive IT consulting services, our team of experts is equipped to handle any challenge. Trust us to deliver top-notch solutions that drive success and growth in the rapidly evolving IT landscape.
